1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:03,150
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:03,150 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 18]

5
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:13,450
No wonder my divination last night warned me

6
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,250
about a backstabber on this trip.

7
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:24,580
Be cautious.

8
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,530
Xiguang,

9
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,170
the Outcast Tomb

10
00:01:47,390 --> 00:01:49,010
is where demons from overseas are interred.

11
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,730
As they're our enemies,

12
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:52,450
why bury them formally?

13
00:01:56,390 --> 00:01:56,700
Here.

14
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,860
Because Wuyue Court's elders

15
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,090
are benevolent.

16
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,700
They laid all vanquished monsters

17
00:02:06,270 --> 00:02:08,460
to rest in peace.

18
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,810
Why did Zhuyan sneak in?

19
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:12,900
Mourning?

20
00:02:15,390 --> 00:02:17,020
Perhaps Demon Lord Yecha's remains

21
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,220
are buried there.

22
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,090
That's why Zhuyan risked everything to get in.

23
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:26,340
Xiguang,

24
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:31,340
are Yecha's eyes golden?

25
00:02:33,430 --> 00:02:37,620
Demon Lord Yecha is said to be cruel, bloodthirsty,

26
00:02:37,830 --> 00:02:39,020
and masked,

27
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,180
with blazing golden eyes.

28
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:40,780
He killed

29
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,020
ruthlessly.

30
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:21,460
Want a fruit?

31
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:37,220
School days are long past.

32
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:39,970
Drop your icy stare

33
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,460
when traveling.

34
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:42,620
Get along with others.

35
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,570
Got it?

36
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:01,740
[Xingzheng Hall]

37
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:23,810
Uncle.

38
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,180
Well done.

39
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:29,130
Your fire-controlling skill is perfected.

40
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,890
Go into seclusion with me from tomorrow

41
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:36,980
to cultivate the Hua Sect's advanced inner art.

42
00:04:37,830 --> 00:04:38,420
Seclusion?

43
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,100
I thought

44
00:04:40,910 --> 00:04:42,940
we were going to the Outcast Tomb on the White Cliff.

45
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:47,860
The tomb was built 500 years ago

46
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,740
by Wuyue Court's ancestors,

47
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:55,210
deemed useless back then

48
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:58,100
by other immortal sects.

49
00:04:58,590 --> 00:05:02,500
Now, Cuixuan has summoned all the immortal sects on White Cliff.

50
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:05,420
Seems disaster looms.

51
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:08,330
The summons is vague.

52
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:11,500
A demonic beast is said to have broken into the tomb.

53
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:13,940
The demon clan

54
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:17,810
has long lurked,

55
00:05:18,700 --> 00:05:21,370
likely laying traps

56
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,540
for us.

57
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:24,300
Then anyone going there

58
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:25,770
will be in danger.

59
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:28,330
As the Sea Calamity draws near,

60
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:31,540
all sects are saving their strength,

61
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:36,940
so few will respond to Wuyue Court.

62
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,060
Cuixuan and his disciples

63
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:43,060
can handle the demons.

64
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,300
Xingzheng Hall won't step in.

65
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,250
We shall wait and observe.

66
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,300
Lifei has weak spirit power,

67
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,660
and she's not Cuixuan's disciple,

68
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:57,770
so she probably won't go.

69
00:06:30,910 --> 00:06:32,060
So this is the Outcast Tomb.

70
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:33,770
What's carved up there?

71
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:39,300
Outcast Tomb for those from countless states and islands overseas.

72
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,940
Countless states and islands?

73
00:06:48,230 --> 00:06:50,740
Could the traps beyond the Ganhua Realm

74
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,100
be linked to the tomb?

75
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,210
What connection

76
00:06:55,910 --> 00:06:57,250
do those islands have with the demon clan?

77
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,660
They originate from there.

78
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,100
Ancient texts record

79
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,690
that there are countless overseas islands,

80
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,100
each with

81
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,690
unique customs,

82
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,370
swarming with demons.

83
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:10,660
The texts only mention foreign folk,

84
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,130
not necessarily demons.

85
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:28,010
The White Cliff is the burial ground of demons,

86
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:31,450
sealed for centuries after its construction.

87
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:35,810
Whoever strays will not return.

88
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:36,980
It's fraught with peril.

89
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,570
This concerns the safety of the Central Plains.

90
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,940
We mustn't take chances.

91
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:49,770
I will follow you to slay demons,

92
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,810
even at the cost of my life.

93
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:55,810
I will follow you to slay demons,

94
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,180
even at the cost of my life.

95
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:28,330
Big trouble!

96
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:29,810
What's wrong?

97
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,940
I just cast a straw divination for this trip

98
00:08:32,230 --> 00:08:33,300
and got the hexagram Earth Over Mountain, Modesty.

99
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,490
Isn't that an auspicious sign?

100
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,180
It's lucky

101
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,060
anywhere else,

102
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,330
but this is

103
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:40,570
a graveyard.

104
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,850
Mountains are within this land,

105
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:43,060
and waters run close beside it.

106
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:44,300
This means

107
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,020
the truth will surface.

108
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,540
Something huge is going to happen.

109
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:48,660
Oh!

110
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:49,420
I need to cast another divination.

111
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:52,610
Really?

112
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:54,940
Lifei.

113
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:57,490
Qin.

114
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,260
Back at Lilie Valley,

115
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,570
I underestimated the enemy

116
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,020
and got corrupted by demonic energy.

117
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:04,660
Sorry to have offended you.

118
00:09:08,540 --> 00:09:09,420
Please grant me

119
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,690
a chance to make amends.

120
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:26,380
It's overgrown and deserted.

121
00:09:26,990 --> 00:09:27,690
Let's stick together.

122
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:42,690
Lifei,

123
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:44,140
something's odd about the bushes.

124
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,730
Stay close.

125
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:46,380
Coming.

126
00:10:03,110 --> 00:10:03,610
Don't touch it.

127
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:05,900
This is Wuyue Court's defensive formation.

128
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:06,970
Once activated,

129
00:10:07,420 --> 00:10:08,970
it'll attack all intruders without discrimination.

130
00:10:12,870 --> 00:10:14,970
Since when have you two grown so close?

131
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:55,060
As expected, Zhuyan's here.

132
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,180
Stay close, Lifei.

133
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:41,260
Xiguang,

134
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:43,660
what hexagram did you just divine?

135
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,210
I didn't even do any divination.

136
00:11:46,710 --> 00:11:48,570
The straws snapped for no reason.

137
00:11:50,830 --> 00:11:51,780
Something's coming.

138
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:23,450
Go now!

139
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,330
Demon!

140
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,660
So you're behind all this.

141
00:12:57,750 --> 00:13:00,020
Worthless immortals,

142
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:03,610
you'll all rot in this tomb today!

143
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,810
Demon, meet your end.

144
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,180
Thank you, Immortal.

145
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:16,060
You've lifted the tomb-sealing talisman

146
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:19,300
that trapped my kin for centuries.

147
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:42,690
It won't work.

148
00:13:43,870 --> 00:13:44,690
A formation looms overhead.

149
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,210
Crafted by Wuyue Court's ancestors

150
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:48,940
masterfully beyond compare,

151
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,940
it's infused with the mystic arts of Qi Men Dun Jia,

152
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:53,420
turning this place

153
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,730
into an inescapable labyrinth.

154
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:02,420
As one of those elders,

155
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,210
can't Elder Cuixuan break it?

156
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,090
Before coming here,

157
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,380
I begged my master to let me

158
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,660
read secret scrolls about the tomb.

159
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:11,660
Elder Cuixuan came here thrice and returned gravely wounded.

160
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:15,540
No one but the formation's creator

161
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:17,730
can break it.

162
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,140
Since he can't break it, did he lead us

163
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,060
to die here?

164
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,090
My master said

165
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,970
Elder Cuixuan acts ruthlessly,

166
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:26,420
risking everything without mercy

167
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,970
for others or himself.

168
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:32,300
Cultivation has stripped him of all compassion.

169
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:33,610
His profound power

170
00:14:33,990 --> 00:14:35,330
lets him survive such gambles,

171
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:36,140
but what about us?

172
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,060
Are we disposable pawns?

173
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,900
No wonder Deng's divination failed.

174
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:43,850
Don't fear.

175
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,850
You'll live.

176
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:56,570
We all will.

177
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:58,330
My master said

178
00:14:58,920 --> 00:14:59,690
no poison or formation

179
00:14:59,710 --> 00:15:00,900
is unbreakable.

180
00:15:01,230 --> 00:15:02,330
I refuse to believe we're trapped forever.

181
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,180
Right.

182
00:15:03,990 --> 00:15:04,940
Man-made barriers

183
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:06,490
always have an exit.

184
00:15:11,470 --> 00:15:12,940
The Life Gate is located in Gen Palace.

185
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:15,690
Come.

186
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:23,380
Lifei.

187
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:29,900
Run now.

188
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,780
You're just an eyesore.

189
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,090
I wouldn't rest in peace

190
00:15:33,350 --> 00:15:34,300
if we perish together.

191
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:35,450
Just accept it.

192
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,570
I'll never leave you.

193
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:38,490
Have you lost your mind?

194
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:53,900
You're corrupted by a demon spirit.

195
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:57,330
We need to purge the demonic energy inside you.

196
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,420
You got corrupted too.

197
00:16:13,110 --> 00:16:14,380
Why channel your spirit energy to me?

198
00:16:22,680 --> 00:16:23,570
Save it for yourself.

199
00:16:24,350 --> 00:16:25,090
Shut up.

200
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:36,610
Lifei.

201
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:45,090
I never thought we'd die side by side.

202
00:16:46,110 --> 00:16:47,570
I'll die with regret.

203
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,060
I thought that if I practiced hard,

204
00:16:53,110 --> 00:16:54,260
I could keep you safe,

205
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:58,570
yet we ended up here.

206
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,090
I'm nothing but a jinx.

207
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:03,610
Why dwell on that now?

208
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,490
You acted for Lu

209
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,140
and had no choice.

210
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:11,070
♪The warmth within my arms♪

211
00:17:11,070 --> 00:17:12,690
Have you forgiven me?

212
00:17:12,690 --> 00:17:15,070
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

213
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:16,180
Not yet.

214
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:17,510
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

215
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:18,340
So,

216
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:20,420
once we die...

217
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:21,710
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

218
00:17:21,710 --> 00:17:22,970
And reach Naihe Bridge...

219
00:17:22,970 --> 00:17:24,600
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

220
00:17:24,600 --> 00:17:26,620
We must drink the Forgetting Soup.

221
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:27,840
♪I can no longer tell you♪

222
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:29,580
Make sure we never cross paths in the next life.

223
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:32,600
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

224
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:33,450
Got it?

225
00:17:33,450 --> 00:17:35,990
♪Utter that line♪

226
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:36,770
I won't.

227
00:17:36,770 --> 00:17:38,490
♪Knowing love and hate♪

228
00:17:38,810 --> 00:17:42,730
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

229
00:17:44,090 --> 00:17:45,690
♪I still linger on♪

230
00:17:46,090 --> 00:17:48,400
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

231
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,820
I'll never drink it.

232
00:17:50,690 --> 00:17:54,200
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

233
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,860
You've been a substitute this life,

234
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:58,660
fleeing for your life since ten.

235
00:17:59,100 --> 00:18:00,290
Homeless,

236
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:01,900
starving,

237
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:05,140
living worse off than me.

238
00:18:05,850 --> 00:18:07,530
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

239
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:09,360
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

240
00:18:09,360 --> 00:18:10,450
What's there

241
00:18:10,470 --> 00:18:11,940
for you to cling to?

242
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:15,100
Drink it and be reborn sooner.

243
00:18:16,790 --> 00:18:17,730
In this life,

244
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:19,410
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

245
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:20,690
I was treated unfairly.

246
00:18:20,690 --> 00:18:24,090
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

247
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:26,450
Yet life hasn't been entirely cruel.

248
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:31,070
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

249
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,050
I have Lu

250
00:18:33,710 --> 00:18:34,340
and...

251
00:18:34,340 --> 00:18:38,580
♪Just to keep you safe♪

252
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,210
And you.

253
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:49,180
I'm really lucky enough.

254
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:53,690
♪My breath is about to stop♪

255
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:57,320
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

256
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:58,290
Truth is...

257
00:18:58,290 --> 00:19:00,310
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

258
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:01,660
I don't want to forget you either.

259
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:03,760
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

260
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:06,990
♪I smile as it ends♪

261
00:19:06,990 --> 00:19:09,210
I traveled nonstop with my master since childhood...

262
00:19:09,210 --> 00:19:10,470
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

263
00:19:10,470 --> 00:19:11,860
Never growing close to anyone.

264
00:19:11,930 --> 00:19:14,600
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

265
00:19:14,600 --> 00:19:16,660
You're the first one to get close to me...

266
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:18,450
♪To light your way through the night♪

267
00:19:19,340 --> 00:19:20,900
And the one I care for most

268
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,690
besides my master.

269
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:27,860
I was furious...

270
00:19:28,130 --> 00:19:30,840
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

271
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,340
Because I trusted you,

272
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:35,100
but you lied to me.

273
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:37,090
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

274
00:19:37,370 --> 00:19:40,330
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

275
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:42,340
Still,

276
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:44,090
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

277
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:46,490
when you took my pain away...

278
00:19:46,490 --> 00:19:47,570
♪I wish you well♪

279
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,250
My heart broken.

280
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:53,970
I feared for you when you

281
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,690
shielded me from harm.

282
00:19:55,690 --> 00:19:56,850
♪You're still screaming♪

283
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:58,340
Now...

284
00:19:58,340 --> 00:20:00,160
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

285
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,100
I understand the line from the storybook.

286
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:04,960
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

287
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,100
Love blooms unawares.

288
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,840
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

289
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:09,770
Deepening without end.

290
00:20:09,770 --> 00:20:15,800
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

291
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:20,080
♪To wander with you♪

292
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,420
Xiuyuan!

293
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:39,530
Xiuyuan!

294
00:22:58,750 --> 00:23:00,380
Demon chants?

295
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,580
Could it be...?

296
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:33,450
Lifei,

297
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,010
why is your spirit power so faint?

298
00:23:35,710 --> 00:23:36,620
What's wrong?

299
00:23:37,310 --> 00:23:38,140
Where is Lei?

300
00:23:48,510 --> 00:23:49,050
Watch out!

301
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:08,100
It's Demon Lord!

302
00:24:09,100 --> 00:24:10,250
Demon Lord Yecha has revived!

303
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:04,180
Lifei, it's too dangerous here.

304
00:25:04,310 --> 00:25:05,050
Let's leave at once.

305
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:09,340
Lifei!

306
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:39,820
Xiuyuan,

307
00:25:44,750 --> 00:25:45,860
it's Lifei.

308
00:25:51,030 --> 00:25:51,730
Xiuyuan,

309
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,770
don't you recognize me?

310
00:26:05,230 --> 00:26:06,210
Xiuyuan.

311
00:26:34,470 --> 00:26:35,340
Master,

312
00:26:35,470 --> 00:26:38,340
why do those spirits keep pestering me?

313
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:40,340
You're different from others.

314
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:43,580
They crave your hair

315
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:45,140
and blood.

316
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:06,120
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

317
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:08,940
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

318
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:12,720
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

319
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:15,160
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

320
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:19,680
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

321
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,760
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

322
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:24,880
♪No calamity can rival♪

323
00:27:25,280 --> 00:27:28,320
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

324
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:33,940
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

325
00:27:34,700 --> 00:27:36,940
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

326
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:40,420
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

327
00:27:41,060 --> 00:27:43,340
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

328
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:47,620
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

329
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:50,260
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

330
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:53,740
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

331
00:27:54,460 --> 00:27:56,660
♪Reign supreme♪

332
00:27:57,680 --> 00:28:00,960
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

333
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:10,520
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

334
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:13,520
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

335
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:17,320
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

336
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:19,960
♪Yet I remain silent♪

337
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:24,360
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

338
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:27,440
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

339
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:29,960
♪The grand chapter is rewritten♪

340
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:33,280
♪Startling the whole world♪

341
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:38,360
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

342
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:41,800
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

343
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:45,120
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

344
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:48,200
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

345
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:52,320
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

346
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:55,600
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

347
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:58,560
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

348
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:01,720
♪Reign supreme♪

349
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:06,520
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

350
00:29:07,080 --> 00:29:09,520
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

351
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,560
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

352
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,080
♪Break through the waves♪

353
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:16,000
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

354
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:20,040
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

355
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:23,040
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

356
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:26,760
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

357
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:29,640
♪And falling petals♪

358
00:29:30,230 --> 00:29:31,010
Lifei!

359
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:34,520
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

360
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,100
Fish!

361
00:29:54,990 --> 00:29:55,620
Run!

362
00:30:19,990 --> 00:30:20,860
Don't overthink it.

363
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:23,250
You're so weak

364
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:24,860
that you were possessed by the demonic energy,

365
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:26,940
like being haunted.

366
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,340
It's nothing serious.

367
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,340
Don't

368
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:51,580
misinterpret what I did.

369
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:53,690
I was only saving you.

370
00:31:01,230 --> 00:31:02,050
This scent...

371
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,100
This way.

372
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:39,140
What's wrong?

373
00:32:24,990 --> 00:32:26,490
The aura of the Divine Tree.

374
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:30,620
It's really here.

375
00:32:38,270 --> 00:32:39,340
I think I saw it

376
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,340
somewhere before.

377
00:32:50,990 --> 00:32:52,210
This scent is the same as Lifei's.

378
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:55,940
Could I be Yecha?

379
00:32:59,510 --> 00:33:00,010
No,

380
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,100
I've never hurt Lifei.

381
00:33:07,030 --> 00:33:07,690
Xiuyuan,

382
00:33:08,270 --> 00:33:10,010
this wound looks like it was torn off.

383
00:33:16,030 --> 00:33:16,940
What are you doing?

384
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,580
The aura is gone.

385
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,010
Lifei!

386
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:38,570
Lifei.

387
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:39,780
Lifei.

388
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:44,900
Where have you two been?

389
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,010
Are you alright?

390
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:53,530
We're fine.

391
00:35:00,070 --> 00:35:00,570
Master,

392
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:02,610
the tomb sank into the sea,

393
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:04,530
so the demon threat should be gone.

394
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,420
The White Cliff lies in ruins,

395
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:09,740
yet we found no trace of the Demon Lord's corpse.

396
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:12,010
I cannot rest easy.

397
00:35:12,990 --> 00:35:14,530
This tomb disaster means

398
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:17,300
the demon clan will strike again.

399
00:35:18,630 --> 00:35:20,260
Send word to all immortal sects

400
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:22,220
across the nine states to prepare.

401
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:23,300
Understood.

402
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:46,860
Lifei.

403
00:35:52,990 --> 00:35:55,260
I told you the hexagram Earth Over Mountain, Modesty was ill-omened.

404
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:56,450
Earth over mountain

405
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:57,130
signals a great shock.

406
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:59,530
The White Cliff collapsed.

407
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:04,900
Do you think

408
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:07,900
Demon Lord Yecha perished?

409
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:16,700
I once thought my master's tales

410
00:36:17,590 --> 00:36:19,740
of Yecha were overblown,

411
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:21,170
but now I know

412
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:24,530
they were not.

413
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:25,900
You know what?

414
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,610
When his gaze fell on me,

415
00:36:27,990 --> 00:36:29,820
my legs froze.

416
00:36:32,030 --> 00:36:33,300
Luckily,

417
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:35,820
he just revived

418
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:37,170
with power yet to return.

419
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:38,940
Otherwise...

420
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:42,490
Xiguang,

421
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:46,300
did Yecha truly slaughter countless souls?

422
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:48,700
He slaughtered countless people,

423
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:51,130
like a nightmare for all the immortal sects.

424
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:10,380
Xiguang,

425
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:12,300
have you seen

426
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,780
a huge transparent fish?

427
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:19,300
There's a fish in the Northern Ocean

428
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,780
named Kun.

429
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,420
Its size

430
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,010
is beyond imagination.

431
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,820
You saw something

432
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,610
no mortal has ever witnessed.

433
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:29,820
Legends say the Kun fish comes from overseas.

434
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:30,940
It's a sacred spirit

435
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,820
and is rarely seen.

436
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,650
Are those rock piles

437
00:37:54,110 --> 00:37:55,940
linked to Master?

438
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,740
Whose severed arm

439
00:37:58,550 --> 00:37:59,610
was it?

440
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,820
Jiang Lifei.

441
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,820
Why come here alone?

442
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:15,940
I lost

443
00:38:16,590 --> 00:38:18,220
my Xiaying Sword,

444
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,860
and it was forged specially by my master.

445
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:22,170
I dare not return

446
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:24,490
if I can't find it.

447
00:38:27,990 --> 00:38:29,010
Where did you drop it?

448
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:31,700
I don't know.

449
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:33,050
Everything was a mess yesterday.

450
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:35,570
Those demons kept chasing me,

451
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:38,650
and I don't know where I dropped it.

452
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:45,340
Where is it?

453
00:38:51,630 --> 00:38:53,170
Yangling told me

454
00:38:53,550 --> 00:38:55,900
you were there when Yecha appeared,

455
00:38:56,220 --> 00:38:58,740
but he lost sight of you during the escape.

456
00:39:02,150 --> 00:39:03,490
Where did you go afterward?

457
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:09,300
My cultivation is weak,

458
00:39:10,220 --> 00:39:13,050
and Qin vanished at once.

459
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:25,220
Found it!

460
00:39:29,110 --> 00:39:29,900
I found it.

461
00:39:37,510 --> 00:39:38,650
Yecha has returned,

462
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:40,300
and the demon clan stirs restlessly.

463
00:39:40,700 --> 00:39:41,900
Facing the Sea Calamity,

464
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:43,610
the Central Plains face grave danger.

465
00:39:44,360 --> 00:39:46,780
I hereby invite all immortals

466
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:48,650
to Duanming City by the East Sea

467
00:39:48,990 --> 00:39:51,090
for the Shanhai Gathering.

468
00:39:52,110 --> 00:39:55,220
Immortal Cuixuan, we await your arrival with your disciples.

469
00:39:57,450 --> 00:39:59,640
[Duanming City]

470
00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:10,970
Aren't people here afraid of spirits?

471
00:40:10,990 --> 00:40:11,860
Not at all.

472
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:14,170
Sea Sects excel at taming them.

473
00:40:14,590 --> 00:40:15,220
Every spirit

474
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,820
you see here

475
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,340
serves humans.

476
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:20,130
So in Duanming City,

477
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,650
humans and monsters coexist.

478
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:23,420
It's a unique sight of the Central Plains.

479
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:29,820
Elder Cuixuan,

480
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,220
Qin,

481
00:40:32,470 --> 00:40:33,860
my father awaits you

482
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:35,340
at Luxin Hall of Wanxian Sect.

483
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:36,050
This way.

484
00:40:36,510 --> 00:40:37,700
Many thanks, Ms. Shen.

485
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:44,490
Lifei,

486
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,940
congratulations on joining Wuyue Court as you wished.

487
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:49,420
Credit goes to the masters' teaching.

488
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:51,450
Where's Mr. Mo?

489
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,090
Fearing you'd take Yanfan away,

490
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:55,340
we sent him on an overseas task early.

491
00:40:58,070 --> 00:41:00,170
Didn't you want to break the Fragrance Bond?

492
00:41:00,700 --> 00:41:01,260
What?

493
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:02,420
Made up now?

494
00:41:04,550 --> 00:41:05,220
Where's Gelin?

495
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:07,860
She left on business with Lu Li.

496
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:09,340
She said

497
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:10,340
she'll come to you later.

498
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:12,340
Will you head to Wanxian Sect with me,

499
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:13,300
or wander around?

500
00:41:13,700 --> 00:41:14,260
Walk around.

501
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,380
Lifei,

502
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:20,450
want candied hawthorns?

503
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,860
Fine, you take them.

504
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,010
Sir, two, please.

505
00:41:24,470 --> 00:41:24,860
Okay.

506
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,420
- How much? - Here you are.

507
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:30,530
There's an aromatic shop.

508
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,300
Zhaomin would love it.

509
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:40,130
You only care about her, not me.

510
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:50,650
[Wanxian Sect]
Yecha'd been slain by ancient immortals,

511
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:53,260
yet revived with evil arts,

512
00:41:53,470 --> 00:41:54,970
filled with raging resentment.

513
00:41:55,990 --> 00:41:58,650
Recent disturbances in the mountain-sea barrier

514
00:41:59,220 --> 00:42:02,050
are likely tied to his return.

515
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:05,610
The barrier was built by Wuyue Court's ancestors.

516
00:42:05,990 --> 00:42:07,420
A catastrophe looms.

517
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:10,940
We must protect the barrier at all costs.

518
00:42:12,150 --> 00:42:13,420
Since the barrier lies off the East Sea,

519
00:42:13,470 --> 00:42:14,940
let disciples of both sects

520
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:17,130
patrol nearby islands

521
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:18,900
during this gathering

522
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,010
to root out dangers.

523
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,650
Humans and spirits coexist here.

524
00:42:23,630 --> 00:42:26,220
Shen, do not let your guard down.

525
00:42:37,070 --> 00:42:37,740
Tongzhou?

526
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:38,510
[The Eternal Fragrance]

527
00:42:38,510 --> 00:42:40,720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

528
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:57,020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

529
00:42:57,180 --> 00:43:00,700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

530
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:04,340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

531
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:07,940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

532
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:11,580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

533
00:43:11,980 --> 00:43:15,260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

534
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:18,900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

535
00:43:18,940 --> 00:43:21,940
♪Utter that line♪

536
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:24,140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

537
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:28,620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

538
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,420
♪I still linger on♪

539
00:43:31,580 --> 00:43:35,860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

540
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:40,540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

541
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:44,140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

542
00:43:44,220 --> 00:43:47,660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

543
00:43:47,940 --> 00:43:51,180
♪I wish you well♪

544
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:53,060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

545
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:57,900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

546
00:43:58,500 --> 00:44:00,580
♪You're still screaming♪

547
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:05,220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

548
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:09,820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

549
00:44:10,060 --> 00:44:13,020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

550
00:44:13,140 --> 00:44:15,020
♪Leaping straight into♪

551
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:19,900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

552
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:23,660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

553
00:44:30,100 --> 00:44:33,420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

554
00:44:33,540 --> 00:44:37,060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

555
00:44:37,180 --> 00:44:40,620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

556
00:44:40,780 --> 00:44:43,980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

557
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:47,820
♪I smile as it ends♪

558
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:51,620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

559
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:55,220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

560
00:44:55,380 --> 00:44:58,500
♪To light your way through the night♪

561
00:44:58,580 --> 00:45:00,620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

562
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:05,100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

563
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,900
♪I still linger on♪

564
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:12,340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

565
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:17,020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

566
00:45:17,100 --> 00:45:20,300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

567
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:22,460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

568
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:26,940
